subject: Football
College Athletics
organizations: Rutgers, The State University of New Jersey
lead_paragraph: Rutgers remained unbeaten Sunday night, holding off Connecticut before a crowd of 41, 077 and improving to 8-0 over all, 3-0 in the Big East.
